    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ji_si_han",
      "speaker_name": "铁木真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ji_si_han",
      "speaker_name": "铁木真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你用我金刀，为我杀敌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "枝击白猿",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "华筝就不言语了，笑吟吟的望着他，过了一会，从怀里摸出了一块手帕，打了两个结，向他抛掷过去，叫道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "华筝微笑道：",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖一呆，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "华筝凝视着他，柔声道：",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖摇摇头，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "华筝",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "了一声，本来满脸红晕，突然间转成怒色，说道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "华筝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你瞧这白雕多可怜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "华筝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "它上去干什么⋯⋯",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "的声音说",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可敬！可敬！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拾起长剑，又练了起来，练了半天，这一招",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仍毫无进步，正自焦躁，忽听得身后一个声音冷冷的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖收剑回顾，见说话的正是那头梳三髻的道士，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那道士叫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看清楚了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 776,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "华筝又惊又喜，忙道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 784,
      "line_end": 784
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "华筝解下腰带，把每头小雕的一只脚缚住，喜孜孜的捧了，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 788,
      "line_end": 788
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "华筝道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "华筝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那道士道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "华筝笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 796
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "华筝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那道士微笑道：",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 796
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "华筝满心欢喜，对郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 798,
      "line_end": 798
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你⋯⋯请你，你别走。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 804
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "道士笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你向我磕头干什么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那道士微笑道：",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "道士道：",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 814
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我⋯⋯我上不去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 822
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "转念又想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 826,
      "line_end": 826
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想到这里，望着崖顶出了一会神，就撇下了这件事，提起长剑，把",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 828,
      "line_end": 828
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那道人叫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "缚好了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 868,
      "line_end": 868
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "缚好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 868,
      "line_end": 868
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖提高声音再答：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 870,
      "line_end": 870
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那道人仍没听见，过了片刻，那道人笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 870,
      "line_end": 870
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 884,
      "line_end": 884
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那道人笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 884,
      "line_end": 884
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 894,
      "line_end": 894
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那道人笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 896,
      "line_end": 896
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 898,
      "line_end": 898
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那道人道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 898,
      "line_end": 898
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么他也知道这回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 904,
      "line_end": 904
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖应道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 908,
      "line_end": 908
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 908,
      "line_end": 908
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 914,
      "line_end": 914
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那道人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 916,
      "line_end": 916
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖大奇，心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 920,
      "line_end": 920
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖更是奇怪，依言拨去积雪，横卧在大石之上。那道人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 926,
      "line_end": 926
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个老年牧人神色严肃，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 994,
      "line_end": 994
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "韩宝驹奇道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 994,
      "line_end": 994
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老牧人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 996,
      "line_end": 996
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "另一个牧人笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 996,
      "line_end": 996
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老牧人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 998,
      "line_end": 998
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_cong",
      "speaker_name": "朱聪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他那里学来这般高明的轻身功夫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1020,
      "line_end": 1020
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金雁功",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1026,
      "line_end": 1026
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金雁功",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1030,
      "line_end": 1030
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_xiao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "韩小莹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "靖儿，你下来让三师父替你吧。",
